<p><strong>Our Collection of Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>BOUND ROUND will collect information that does personally identify you, including but not limited to including your name, country you call home, photograph, email address and date of birth should you wish to establish a User Account (“Personal Information”).</p>
<p>Personal Information is collected to assist BOUND ROUND with continually improving its products where possible and to enhance your use of the Website.</p>
<p><strong>Storage and Security of Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>BOUND ROUND will use its reasonable endeavours to maintain the security of your Personal Information. BOUND ROUND requires staff and service providers to respect the confidentiality of Personal Information. However, due to the nature of the Internet, we cannot guarantee that Personal Information will always be secure either during its transmission to BOUND ROUND or from unauthorised access during storage and you therefore disclose your Personal Information to BOUND ROUND at your own risk. To assist BOUND ROUND with protecting all Personal Information, we request that you contact BOUND ROUND immediately if you become aware or have reason to believe of any unauthorised use of your Personal Information in connection with the Website.</p>
<p><strong>Use and Disclosure of Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>BOUND ROUND reserves the right to disclose Personal Information to third parties including to retailers located both in and outside Australia (“BOUND ROUND Partners”). BOUND ROUND Partners are not authorised to contact Users directly and your email address will not be shared. BOUND ROUND requests all BOUND ROUND Partners to comply with a similar privacy policy. Please contact BOUND ROUND if you believe that any BOUND ROUND Partner has used Personal Information in a manner that has been detrimental to you.</p>
<p>The Personal Information of children under the age of 13 will not be shared.</p>
<p><strong>Access to Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>BOUND ROUND will use its reasonable endeavours to keep Personal Information current and accurate. BOUND ROUND encourages you to correct any Personal Information that is inaccurate by amending your details on the Website. If you are unable to amend or delete your Personal Information you may Contact Us and we will use reasonable endeavours to provide, amend or delete your Personal Information within a reasonable period of receipt of your request. If applicable, any legal requirement on BOUND ROUND to maintain certain records concerning your Personal Information must prevail over any of your requests.</p>
<p><strong>Children’s Privacy</strong></p>
<p>BOUND ROUND requests that a child’s parent or legal guardian consent to their child’s use of the Website and explain this Privacy Policy to them.</p>
